      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:39:4",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَمِيرُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ ( عليه السلام ) يُقْطَعُ سَارِقُ الْمَوْتَى كَمَا يُقْطَعُ سَارِقُ الْأَحْيَاءِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Habeen Bin Al Hassan, from Muhammad Bin Al Waleed, from Amro Bin Sabit, from Abu Al Jaroud, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The thief of the dead would be cut just as the thief of the living is cut’."
        ]
